{
  "$schema": "Sample editor fixture consumed by /perf-fixture and editor-perf-trace.mjs.",
  "$comment": "tid/pid intentionally omitted: keeping them empty short-circuits EditorSessionService's Firestore-subscription effect, so the perf trace measures pure render/interaction work.",
